item.title: CVE-2023-5098|2024-08-02T07:44:53.809Z -- unknown -- campaign%20monitor%20forms%20by%20optin%20cat
item.description: The Campaign Monitor Forms by Optin Cat WordPress plugin before 2.5.6 does not prevent users with low privileges (like subscribers) from overwriting any options on a site with the string "true", which could lead to a variety of outcomes, including DoS.
